high_descs: Turn right and walk towards the door, then hang a right and walk up to the wooden dresser.
Pick up the leftmost black statue off of the wooden dresser.
Turn left and walk over to the lamp that is to the left of the wooden dresser.
Turn on the light of the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine a black statue in the light of a tall lamp.

high_descs: walk over to the front of the dresser where the statues are
pick up the statue from the dresser
walk the statue over to the lamp on the stand and raise the statue
turn the lamp on to look at the statue
anns.task_desc: Take a statue from the dresser to the lamp then examine it up to the light

high_descs: Move right then right again and go straight to the wood end table
Pick up the statue on top of the end table
Move slightly left to face the floor lamp to the left of the end table
anns.task_desc: Turn on a lamp while holding a statue
